  "text": "Among the main features offered by ROOT-Sim we can mention completely transparent recoverability of the state of the LPs achieved through proper hooking of dynamic memory allocation/release [CITATION_1] , plus ad-hoc code instrumentation schemes that allow incremental determination of dirty state portions [CITATION_2] and that, ultimately, allow dynamical switch between different state log/restore schemes depending on the proper dynamics of the application layer [CITATION_3] .",
